:

1. *Onog* puta smo proveli prijatno vreme. (That time we spent a pleasant time.)
2. *Onog* dana se desio nesrećan događaj. (That day an unfortunate event happened.)
3. Svi su se veoma radovali *onom* uspehu. (Everyone was very happy about that success.)
4. Ona je bila vrlo ljuta zbog *onog* događaja. (She was very angry about that event.)
5. Moj otac je bio oduševljen *onim* činom. (My father was delighted with that act.)